title: Herp Alpert & The Tijuana Brass - Very Best Of 1986 TQMP
description:
I guess for the majority of us this is our parents' music, which is probably enough reason to hate it to death ;)
I could not resist taking it home from our local public library and checkin' it out. I haven't heard it for 35 years or so but still recognize every single piece. Most of you will probably have the same experience, whether you like it or not ;)

You know what: Carlton from The Fresh Prince of Bel Air might not have such bad taste after all!
